The paper deals with the estimation distortion of a distributed sensing system with orthogonal multiple access, which is a problem in information theory (cs.IT) and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also discusses the use of coding schemes, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM) and networking (cs.NI). Finally, the paper proposes algorithms for optimizing the sensing system, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG).
